PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782821899
OL,3,CHealth Minister launches #5m obesity
OL,4,Cservice
OL,6,FWeight-loss injections will be
OL,7,Favailable free on the NHS in Northern
OL,8,FIreland in a new #5million initiative
OL,9,Fto tackle obesity.
OL,11,FBut the medication - included in the
OL,12,Fnew Regional Obesity Management
OL,13,FService - is to be issued to those
OL,14,Fwith the highest clinical need first,
OL,15,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt said.
OL,17,FIt comes as obesity is identified as
OL,18,Fone of the Northern Ireland's biggest
OL,19,Fpublic health issues, with 65% of
OL,20,Fadults living with obesity or excess
OL,21,Fweight.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
