PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782821899
OL,3,CHealth Minister launches #5m obesity
OL,4,Cservice
OL,6,FWeight loss medication for adult
OL,7,Fpatients will be among approaches in
OL,8,FROMS which is expected to be rolled
OL,9,Fout in early autumn 2026.
OL,11,FMr Nesbitt said the new service will
OL,12,Fhelp improve the lives of many people.
OL,14,FHe added: "Obesity is a significant
OL,15,Fpublic health issue and those living
OL,16,Fwith being overweight or obese are at
OL,17,Fa higher risk of a range of major
OL,18,Fhealth conditions including heart
OL,19,Fdisease, stroke, type 2 diabetes and
OL,20,Fsome cancers," he said.
