PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782821899
OL,3,CHealth Minister launches #5m obesity
OL,4,Cservice
OL,6,F"This service aligns with my vision
OL,7,Ffor the future of Health and Social
OL,8,FCare (HSC), shifting left and bringing
OL,9,Fcare closer to people's front doors,
OL,10,Fas set out in my recently published
OL,11,Fneighbourhood model of health and
OL,12,Fwellbeing."
OL,14,FMr Nesbitt said obesity
OL,15,Fdisproportionately affects those from
OL,16,Fdisadvantaged communities (68%)
OL,17,Fcompared to the least disadvantaged
OL,18,F(62%).
