PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782821899
OL,3,CHealth Minister launches #5m obesity
OL,4,Cservice
OL,6,FHe addad: "The shift from treating ill
OL,7,Fhealth to helping people stay well
OL,8,Fwill support longer, healthier, and
OL,9,Fmore active lives, bringing Northern
OL,10,FIreland in line with the rest of the
OL,11,FUK and improving health outcomes."
OL,13,FROMS is planned to be implemented
OL,14,Falongside the new Obesity Pathway
OL,15,FInnovation Programme which received a
OL,16,F#7 million share of an #85 million
OL,17,Fenvelope from the UK Government and
OL,18,Fpharmaceutical company, Lilly, and
OL,19,Fwill be delivered in partnership with
OL,20,Fthe community and voluntary sector.
